米都死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:01:12.000Z","msg":"你都痴九線<br />\n兩米跪落去到仆街啦"},{"pid":"cacd75c40deb04103e8dda9f6edf964d78e6de71","tid":647432,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"d88a743b437a2d28f192e123135788fa2aacff5f","tid":647432,"uid":19981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6386f5cf46785162d29533339903a5ddc68cf533","tid":647432,"uid":99205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f12822ba7bf7a7e537ed7b4738dee50f5cd574a","tid":647432,"uid":71433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8ce8c921ed24f7f84e1f7bc4a67907d780910900","tid":647432,"uid":135767,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T23:20:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T23:22:23.000Z","msg":"依家已經無人關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:21:35.000Z","msg":"死既唔係女人<br />\n又無後生女遺孀出來喊<br />\n<br />\n當然沒人理"},{"pid":"360a9f552abefedccbec5d48b12783a4500e5e5c","tid":647432,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:26:18.000Z","msg":"釘板同札鐵講得衰d就係個石屎廊起好後就可以離場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}